---
title: Quickdraw Quesadillas with Cilantro-Lime Crema and Tomato Salad
description: This fiesta of flavors will satisfy your craving for Mexican, plus it's vegetarian, so everyone can enjoy! Corn kernels add a bit of sweetness to the mix, and a zingy salad on the side brightens up the dish.
